Package com.example.eventapp.models

Class Facility

java.lang.Object
com.example.eventapp.models.Facility
All Implemented Interfaces:
HasDocumentId
public class Facility extends Object implements HasDocumentId
Represents a Facility that hosts events, including details such as name, description, and photo. Implements the HasDocumentId interface for Firestore integration.
